column2: SELECT TOP # ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY g.specobjid DESC) as RowNumber, s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.zwarning, g.h_beta_flux, g.h_beta_flux_err,g.oiii_#_flux,g.oiii_#_flux_err,g.nii_#_flux,g.nii_#_flux_err,g.h_alpha_flux, g.h_alpha_flux_err FROM GalSpecLine AS g JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid WHERE s.class = &&& AND s.zwarning = # ; WITH MySelectedRows AS ( SELECT TOP # ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY g.specobjid DESC) as RowNumber, s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.zwarning, g.h_beta_flux, g.h_beta_flux_err,g.oiii_#_flux,g.oiii_#_flux_err,g.nii_#_flux,g.nii_#_flux_err,g.h_alpha_flux, g.h_alpha_flux_err FROM GalSpecLine AS g JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid WHERE s.class = &&& AND s.zwarning = # ) SELECT * FROM MySelectedRows  WHERE RowNumber BETWEEN # AND #
